To build Bounded_Model_Checker, 

1) Go inside DAGManager/. Do "make"

2) Go inside Eliminator/. 
   
   Open Makefile.

   The code uses cudd library. Set the variable BDD_PATH in Makefile 
   as the path of cudd library. 

   Do "make"

3) Open makefile in the present directory.

   Set the variable BDD_PATH in makefile 
   as the path of cudd library. 

   Do "make"
 
